Movies Database

1. Initial screen will list all the movies name in the application
2. User can search for particular movie from the search box
3. User can add a movie with the Add Movie feature
    3.a. User can add new actors and producers in the same screen if the existing list does not contain
4. On clicking the movie name from the list, all the details about the movie will be displayed
5. The details of the movie can be edited
    5.a. Actor details can be viewed on clicking the actor name and the details of the actor can be edited on this screen. The same applies for producer details.
6. User can delete the movie with the Delete feature.

Front End:
    Angular 6

Back End: 
    NodeJS
    MongoDB

    Proper validations added.
    Validations are done at both level 
        1. Model level (Mongoose)
        2. Request level (Joi validator)
    
    Validations List:
        Movies: 
            name: {
		`       type: String,
		        required: true
            },
            year_of_release: {
                type: Number,
                required: true
            },
            plot: {
                type: String
            },
            poster: {
                type: String,
                required: true
            },
            actors: [{
                ref : "actors",
                type : ObjectId,
                required: true
            }],
            producer: {
                ref : "producers",
                type : ObjectId,
                required: true
            }
        Actors: 
            name: {
                type: String,
                required: true
            },
            sex: {
                type: String, 
                required: true,
                enum: ['male', 'female', 'third']
            },
            dob: {
                type: String
            },
            bio: {
                type: String
            }
        Producers: 
            name: {
                type: String,
                required: true
            },
            sex: {
                type: String, 
                required: true,
                enum: ['male', 'female', 'third']
            },
            dob: {
                type: String
            },
            bio: {
                type: String
            }    

Devops:
    Dockerised
